# 拜登“急切期待”瑞典加入北约

Author: 半岛电视台

Publisher: Al Jazeera

Published Time: 2023-07-06T02:48:11

Modified Time: 2023-07-06T02:48:11

Description: 美国总统乔·拜登在接待来访的瑞典首相克里斯特松时表示，他“急切期待”该北欧国家加入北约。

Images: ["[2023-07-05T18...](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-07-05T182212Z_1252066000_RC26X1ARSA1F_RTRMADP_3_USA-SWEDEN-1688585586-1688611120.jpg)", "[image-2-16886...](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/image-2-1688611187.jpg)", "[image-3-16886...](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/image-3-1688611272.jpg)"]

